Package org.jlab.epsci.ersap.base

Class ServiceName

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jlab.epsci.ersap.base.ServiceName
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ErsapName
    public class ServiceName
extends java.lang.Object
implements ErsapName
    Unique identifier of a ERSAP service.

    The canonical name for a service has the following structure: 

     <container_canonical_name>:<engine_name>
    Example: 
     10.1.1.1_java:master:SqrRoot
    See Also:
    ContainerName
